{"tid":305140,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"網民選靚港姐 朱千雪「爆冷」拎第一","createTime":"2017-07-01T12:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T10:32:14.000Z","uid":9573,"like":28,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcab33b9deb3182e709210c65248e278a0c8eb56","tid":305140,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"年年港姐初賽都會出現一堆「極品」，搞到個個都對港姐比賽「先扣五十分」，身為娛樂界KOL嘅King Jer，早幾日喺facebook搞咗一個投票，比個機會大家，揀下邊幾個先係心目中最靚嘅港姐！<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19429878_1551660431572482_3925125467656865769_n.png?oh=82c46ee7728750cc5119c8342efc5a09&amp;oe=59C64497\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19429878_1551660431572482_3925125467656865769_n.png%3Foh%3D82c46ee7728750cc5119c8342efc5a09%26oe%3D59C64497&h=02d552a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢日結果出爐喇，估唔到排頭位嘅係2012年季軍朱千雪，講真朱千雪讀緊城大法律博士學位，個人又夠貼地，的確加咗唔少分，不過有網民就話佢：「梁國雄議員，請你立即離開會議廳﹗」學King Jer話：「觀眾緣嘅野解釋唔到嘅。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/006kbjvzly1fh2gvnt45xj30go0gonbj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww3.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F006kbjvzly1fh2gvnt45xj30go0gonbj.jpg&h=9d59d810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n排第二喺1991年冠軍郭藹明，第三名係邱淑貞，「紅姑」鍾楚紅排第四，「十優港姐」麥明詩排第八，至於第九係佘詩曼、第10就係湯洛雯！<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/006kbjvzly1fh2gvr5kq2j30go0gotlj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww3.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F006kbjvzly1fh2gvr5kq2j30go0gotlj.jpg&h=01fe5d7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港TVB資訊台：【十大最靚港姐 李嘉欣排第七】<br />\n網民搞咗《十大最靚港姐》投票，網友投票最靚嘅港姐就係朱千雪喇，佢以約三千票大熱成為最索港姐。咁亞軍就係「美貌與智慧並重」嘅代表人物郭藹明。季軍就有邱淑貞。<br />\n<br />\n1. #朱千雪#（2989票）<br />\n2. #郭藹明#（2479票）<br />\n3. #邱淑貞#（1807票）<br />\n4. #鍾楚紅#（1418票）<br />\n5. #吳婉芳#（1374票）<br />\n6. #袁詠儀#（1018票）<br />\n7. #李嘉欣#（955票）<br />\n8. #麥明詩#（953票）<br />\n9. #佘詩曼#（838票）<br />\n10. #湯洛雯#（639票）"},{"pid":"d95feeb790b4b7d67c508800c858665ebdb39b84","tid":305140,"uid":53498,"like":43,"dislike":20,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢榜嚟,湯洛雯都上到頭十"},{"pid":"e7ee40715fd0dccd287e5c0746c3e4acc76451e1","tid":305140,"uid":92376,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T12:19:27.000Z","msg":"無朱晨麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5457c79329f05a734241b8bf08fcb592ee0b98fd","tid":305140,"uid":64093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T12:22:09.000Z","msg":"譚小環都冇我砒"},{"pid":"60a0ac251bdab1a8829340581cd35ea6e5371b00","tid":305140,"uid":49004,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T12:22:52.000Z","msg":"邱淑貞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c88456cb7f34eb75c97b13ee67007aaba4aa3f0","tid":305140,"uid":32298,"like":60,"dislike":6,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T12:46:01.000Z","msg":"麥明詩都榜上有名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1b6cc184ad83b2777c627371e027019a4b4b32","tid":305140,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:28:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邱淑貞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" 